GL Routine</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"5-결과물\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-%EA%B2%B0%EA%B3%BC%EB%AC%BC\" aria-label=\"5 결과물 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. 결과물</h4>\n<p><img src=\"/edcd33897f9d64920087054d4d7ea103/opengl_4_1.gif\" alt=\"Image\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"6-전체코드-확인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6-%EC%A0%84%EC%B2%B4%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"6 전체코드 확인 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6. 전체코드 확인</h4>\n<script src=\"https://gist.github.com/paroblow/f0e6cbb2487cf817653993f923111ce9.js\"></script>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/opengl-4","tagSlugs":["/tag/open-gl/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2018-12-20T23:34:00.001Z","description":"","tags":["OpenGL"],"title":"OpenGL 강좌 _ 4강. 2D Animation","socialImage":"/media/opengl_4_0.png"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/ope